  <entry>
    <title type="html"><![CDATA[CentOS常用配置]]></title>
    <link href="http://hiberabyss.github.io/blog/20130711/centos/"/>
    <updated>2013-07-11T19:47:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://hiberabyss.github.io/blog/20130711/centos</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文记录对CentOS的一些配置方法。</p>

<!--more-->

<h2 id="section">包管理</h2>
<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
<span class="line-number">5</span>
<span class="line-number">6</span>
<span class="line-number">7</span>
<span class="line-number">8</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class=""><span class="line">#安装包
</span><span class="line">rpm -ivh your.rpm --force --nodeps
</span><span class="line">#升级包
</span><span class="line">rpm -Uvh your.rpm --force --nodeps
</span><span class="line">#卸载包
</span><span class="line">rpm -e --nodeps uninstall.rpm
</span><span class="line">#查询已安装的包
</span><span class="line">rpm -qa pattern</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<h2 id="section-1">服务管理</h2>
<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class=""><span class="line">#设置服务开机启动
</span><span class="line">chkconfig the-service on
</span><span class="line">#查询某个服务开启状态
</span><span class="line">chkconfig --list the-service</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<h2 id="section-2">修改主机名</h2>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class=""><span class="line">#临时设置主机名为the-name，重启后失效；需要重新登陆
</span><span class="line">hostname the-name</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>编辑文件<code>/etc/sysconfig/network</code>，对如下字段做修改：</p>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class=""><span class="line">HOSTNAME=the-name</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<h2 id="section-3">网络接口配置</h2>
<p>修改<code>/etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifconfig-eth0</code>文件进行相应的网络设置，其中<code>eth0</code>可以用相应的网络接口名称代替，如果相应的文件不存在，则可以创建一个新的文件：</p>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
<span class="line-number">5</span>
<span class="line-number">6</span>
<span class="line-number">7</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="bash"><span class="line"><span class="nv">DEVICE</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;eth0&quot;</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">BOOTPROTO</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;static&quot;</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">HWADDR</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="s2">&quot;网卡物理地址&quot;</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="c">#如果BOOTPROTO设置为dhcp，则不需要下面的设置</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">IPADDR</span><span class="o">=</span>ip地址
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">NETMASK</span><span class="o">=</span>子网掩码
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">GATEWAY</span><span class="o">=</span>网关
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>修改文件<code>/etc/resolv.conf</code>可以配置DNS服务器：</p>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
<span class="line-number">5</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="bash"><span class="line"><span class="c">#国内公用DNS服务器</span>
</span><span class="line">nameserver 114.114.114.114
</span><span class="line"><span class="c">#Google公用dns服务器</span>
</span><span class="line">nameserver 8.8.8.8
</span><span class="line">nameserver 8.8.4.4
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>修改文件<code>/etc/udev/rules.d/70-persistent-net.rules</code>可以根据相应的<code>mac</code>地址修改网络接口的显示名称。</p>

<h2 id="section-4">本地源</h2>
<p>将iso文件挂载到目录<code>/mnt/iso</code>，并写入到文件<code>/etc/fstab</code>中</p>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="bash"><span class="line">mount -o loop /root/iso/CentOS-6.3-x86_64-bin-DVD1.iso /mnt/dvd1/
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>新建文件<code>/etc/yum.repos.d/locale.repo</code>文件，写入一下内容：</p>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
<span class="line-number">3</span>
<span class="line-number">4</span>
<span class="line-number">5</span>
<span class="line-number">6</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="bash"><span class="line"><span class="o">[</span>locale<span class="o">]</span>
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">name</span><span class="o">=</span>CentOS-6.3 - DVD1
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">baseurl</span><span class="o">=</span>file:///mnt/dvd1/ file:///mnt/dvd2/
</span><span class="line"><span class="nb">enable</span><span class="o">=</span>1
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">gpcheck</span><span class="o">=</span>1
</span><span class="line"><span class="nv">gpgkey</span><span class="o">=</span>file:///mnt/dvd1/RPM-GPG-KEY-CentOS-6
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>

<p>把目录<code>/etc/yum.repos.d/</code>下<code>CentOS-Base.repo</code>文件和<code>CentOS-Debuginfo.repo</code>文件更改后缀名，否则会报错。</p>

<p>或者利用如下方式使用<code>yum</code></p>

<div class="bogus-wrapper"><notextile><figure class="code"><figcaption><span></span></figcaption><div class="highlight"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre class="line-numbers"><span class="line-number">1</span>
<span class="line-number">2</span>
</pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="bash"><span class="line"><span class="c">#只使用本地源</span>
</span><span class="line">yum --disablerepo<span class="o">=</span>/* --enablerepo<span class="o">=</span>locale install
</span></code></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure></notextile></div>
]]></content>
